parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the emergency brake caliper can cause the brake to stick, leading to unexpected movement of the vehicle when parked on a slope, increasing the risk of a collision.
symptoms: The emergency brake caliper is stuck
the brake pedal is hard to operate
the brake fails to stop the car
the parking brake is required to stop the vehicle
the engine RPM increases dramatically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brake pedal to be excessively hard to operate, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brake pedal is hard to operate
the brake fails to stop the car
the engine RPM increases dramatically
the transmission needs to be shifted to neutral to bring the RPM to normal velocity.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission whine and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Audible whine from the transmission when in motion
transmission disengages while driving
loss of power
engine racing
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
including the engine light
low tire pressure
airbag
and traction control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Malfunction and Loss of Acceleration
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission malfunction and loss of acceleration can cause the vehicle to stall or hesitate, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Failure to accelerate when depressing the accelerator pedal
engine RPMs increase
SCBS warning and engine check required displayed on the message board
transmission malfunction
and warning lights illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration and brake failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, making it difficult to stop or control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle fails to stop when depressing the brake pedal
feeling of brakes being bled off
engine RPMs increase
and transmission shifts into neutral.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to inadequate protection in the event of a collision, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning indicator flashes on and off
the front passenger airbag off indicator remains illuminated
the airbag deploys incorrectly
the airbag fails to inflate
the airbag inflates unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to properly address the Takata airbag recall can lead to inadequate protection in the event of a collision, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Difficulty in arranging a repair
lack of communication from the manufacturer or dealer
no record of the recall
failure to receive a recall notice.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Repair for Recalled Airbag Inflator
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of repair for the recalled airbag inflator can lead to prolonged exposure to the risk of airbag system failure, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Waiting for months for the dealer to repair the recalled airbag inflator
lack of communication from the dealer
uncertainty about the safety of the vehicle.
